      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-cod-dcf-spt    =    zero
                     move  w-lds-000
                          (001:11)        to   w-det-cod-dcf-spt
                     move  w-lds-000
                          (012:05)        to   w-det-cod-dcf-spg
                     go to xcv-trt-pds-900.
